arStrings.szText: A Umbaru woman, chosen by the spirits, prepares for a daunting initiation rite.
A mysterious stranger named Sutsara has asked me to gather Goatmen heads so that she might perform a ritual allowing her to become the vessel of a Goatman-hunting spirit.
A mysterious stranger named Sutsara prepares a ritual to become the vessel of a Goatman-hunting spirit. I should speak with her to begin the ritual.

A mysterious stranger named Sutsara prepares a ritual to become the vessel of a Goatman-hunting spirit. Now that I have gathered the Goatmen heads, I should place them on spikes around the altar Sutsara spoke of.
Place the Goatman heads at the altar
The ritual was successful and Sutsara has transformed into a Goatman-hunting predator. I've found her in combat with a pack of Goatmen and should join her in defeating the creatures.
The creature returned to the camp and transformed back into Sutsara. I should speak with her now that she has returned to her human-shape.
After slaughtering a group of Goatmen, creature known as "Etsuk Supa" that was once Sutsara has fled towards her camp. I should follow her there.
A mysterious stranger named Sutsara has begun a ritual to become the vessel of a Goatman-hunting spirit. I should watch her perform the ritual and see what happens.
After completing the ritual, Sutsara cryptically spoke of hunting the Goatmen before vanishing. I should search the area for any signs of her.
